                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d358">
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Minister of Panama</gloss> to the
                            <gloss type="to">Secretary of State</gloss>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Habana</hi>
                        </placeName> (<date
                            ana="#date_undated-inferred-from-document-content-and-sibling-dates"
                            calendar="gregorian" notAfter="1909-01-31T23:59:59-05:00"
                            notBefore="1909-01-30T00:00:00-05:29">undated</date>).<lb/>(Received
                        January 31, 1909.)</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Secretary Arango cables me that both treaties have been ratified by Panama.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Arosemena</hi>.</signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
